table.name: Author
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE Author ( ReferenceUUID varchar, SequenceNumber int, LastName varchar COLLATE SenteLocalizedNoCase, ForeNames varchar COLLATE SenteLocalizedNoCase, ForeNamesAsInitials varchar COLLATE SenteLocalizedNoCase, Role varchar COLLATE SenteLocalizedNoCase, AspectValue varchar COLLATE SenteLocalizedNoCase );

index.name: AuthorPK
index.ddl: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX AuthorPK ON Author( ReferenceUUID, SequenceNumber );

index.name: AuthorAspectValueToRef
index.ddl: CREATE INDEX AuthorAspectValueToRef ON Author( AspectValue, ReferenceUUID );

index.name: RefToAuthorAspectValue
index.ddl: CREATE INDEX RefToAuthorAspectValue ON Author( ReferenceUUID, AspectValue );
